<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %></title>

    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="student-page">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-primary">
      <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
          <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Anti-Ragging Portal
        </a>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm">
          <i class="fas fa-arrow-left me-2"></i>Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container my-5">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
          <div class="card shadow-lg border-0">
            <div class="card-header bg-info text-white py-4">
              <h2 class="mb-0">
                <i class="fas fa-balance-scale me-2"></i>Anti-Ragging Rules &
                Regulations
              </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-5">
              <div class="alert alert-info mb-4">
                <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i>
                <strong>What is Ragging?</strong> Ragging constitutes any act
                causing, or likely to cause, physical, psychological or
                physiological harm or apprehension, embarrassment, or trauma to
                a student.
              </div>

              <h4 class="fw-bold text-primary mb-3">
                UGC Definition of Ragging
              </h4>
              <p>According to UGC Regulations 2009, ragging includes:</p>

              <div class="row g-3 mb-4">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <div class="card border-danger h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h6 class="text-danger fw-bold">
                        <i class="fas fa-hand-paper me-2"></i>Physical Ragging
                      </h6>
                      <ul class="small">
                        <li>Any act of physical assault</li>
                        <li>Forced physical exercises</li>
                        <li>Stripping or forcing obscene acts</li>
                        <li>Any form of physical abuse</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <div class="card border-warning h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h6 class="text-warning fw-bold">
                        <i class="fas fa-brain me-2"></i>Mental/Psychological
                        Ragging
                      </h6>
                      <ul class="small">
                        <li>Teasing, abusing, threatening</li>
                        <li>Intimidation and harassment</li>
                        <li>Asking to do menial tasks</li>
                        <li>Creating psychological pressure</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <div class="card border-danger h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h6 class="text-danger fw-bold">
                        <i class="fas fa-laptop me-2"></i>Cyber Ragging
                      </h6>
                      <ul class="small">
                        <li>Online harassment and bullying</li>
                        <li>Sharing morphed/private images</li>
                        <li>Trolling on social media</li>
                        <li>Spreading false rumors online</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <div class="card border-danger h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <h6 class="text-danger fw-bold">
                        <i class="fas fa-user-times me-2"></i>Sexual Harassment
                      </h6>
                      <ul class="small">
                        <li>Any form of sexual abuse</li>
                        <li>Obscene gestures or comments</li>
                        <li>Inappropriate touching</li>
                        <li>Gender-based harassment</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <hr class="my-4" />

              <h4 class="fw-bold text-primary mb-3">Institutional Rules</h4>

              <div class="card bg-light mb-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h6 class="fw-bold">Rule 1: Zero Tolerance</h6>
                  <p class="mb-0 small">
                    The institution maintains a strict zero-tolerance policy
                    towards ragging. Any form of ragging is strictly prohibited
                    and will result in severe action.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="card bg-light mb-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h6 class="fw-bold">Rule 2: Mandatory Reporting</h6>
                  <p class="mb-0 small">
                    Every student, faculty member, and staff is required to
                    report any ragging incident immediately. Failure to report
                    is also considered an offense.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="card bg-light mb-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h6 class="fw-bold">Rule 3: Anti-Ragging Affidavit</h6>
                  <p class="mb-0 small">
                    All students must submit an anti-ragging affidavit signed by
                    themselves and their parents/guardians at the time of
                    admission.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="card bg-light mb-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h6 class="fw-bold">Rule 4: Surprise Inspections</h6>
                  <p class="mb-0 small">
                    The Anti-Ragging Squad will conduct surprise inspections in
                    hostels, common areas, and isolated locations to prevent
                    ragging.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="card bg-light mb-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h6 class="fw-bold">Rule 5: Awareness Programs</h6>
                  <p class="mb-0 small">
                    Regular awareness programs and orientations will be
                    conducted for all students to educate about anti-ragging
                    policies.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="card bg-light mb-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h6 class="fw-bold">Rule 6: Immediate Action</h6>
                  <p class="mb-0 small">
                    Upon receiving a complaint, immediate preliminary inquiry
                    will be conducted within 24 hours, and action will be taken
                    within 7 days.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <hr class="my-4" />

              <h4 class="fw-bold text-primary mb-3">
                Student Responsibilities
              </h4>
              <ul>
                <li>Do not participate in any form of ragging</li>
                <li>Report any ragging incident immediately</li>
                <li>Cooperate with authorities during investigations</li>
                <li>Support victims and do not remain silent</li>
                <li>Attend anti-ragging awareness programs</li>
                <li>Follow all institutional guidelines</li>
              </ul>

              <hr class="my-4" />

              <h4 class="fw-bold text-primary mb-3">Safe Zones & Red Zones</h4>

              <div class="row g-3">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <div class="card border-success">
                    <div class="card-header bg-success text-white">
                      <h6 class="mb-0">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle me-2"></i>Safe Zones (Well
                        Monitored)
                      </h6>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <ul class="small mb-0">
                        <li>Library and Reading Rooms</li>
                        <li>Computer Labs</li>
                        <li>Classrooms during class hours</li>
                        <li>Cafeteria/Dining Hall</li>
                        <li>Sports Complex</li>
                        <li>Administrative Offices</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <div class="card border-danger">
                    <div class="card-header bg-danger text-white">
                      <h6 class="mb-0">
                        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i>Red
                        Zones (High Vigilance)
                      </h6>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                      <ul class="small mb-0">
                        <li>Hostel Rooms (especially senior wings)</li>
                        <li>Isolated corridors</li>
                        <li>Parking areas after dark</li>
                        <li>Unlit areas of campus</li>
                        <li>Abandoned buildings</li>
                        <li>Outside campus boundaries</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="alert alert-warning mt-4">
                <h6 class="fw-bold">
                  <i class="fas fa-lightbulb me-2"></i>Remember:
                </h6>
                <ul class="mb-0 small">
                  <li>
                    <strong>Ragging is a CRIME</strong> - Not a tradition or
                    cultural practice
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>You are PROTECTED</strong> - Your identity will be
                    kept confidential
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Speak UP</strong> - Silence encourages offenders
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong>Help Available 24/7</strong> - Multiple channels to
                    report
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div class="text-center mt-4">
                <a href="/complaint/submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg me-2">
                  <i class="fas fa-file-alt me-2"></i>Report Ragging Incident
                </a>
                <a href="/penalties" class="btn btn-outline-danger btn-lg">
                  <i class="fas fa-gavel me-2"></i>View Penalties
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="bg-dark text-white py-3 mt-5">
      <div class="container text-center">
        <p class="mb-0">&copy; 2024 Anti-Ragging Portal</p>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
